{"tid":1896490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連蕭生都支持網上教學？？","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T07:18:40.000Z","uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5287840d9da6a38745487a4b4a05169d72f05063","tid":1896490,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rs6vSFwl150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRs6vSFwl150&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=89387b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rs6vSFwl150</a><br />\n<br />\n10分 48秒<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個好似蕭生咁叻講兩句就拎a既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次唔認同佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有d離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d5db95cc347008b378d1b5847591afba000b3","tid":1896490,"uid":215700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"網上教學真係慳好多時間<br />\n今年無住hall 每日返學來回計埋等車都曬左兩個鐘 返學要見人又要打扮下自己 <br />\n依家就算上8半都可以準時上到 真係起唔到身又可以錄低再慢慢溫返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學就更加唔需要返學校啦 中學自修完全冇難題"},{"pid":"4b08fe7aad50c7b65a3e4857c4d573f62efe96d7","tid":1896490,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"剩係講學術成績：係<br />\n<br />\n但學生返學既價值唔係剩係書本上既知識，大家都明<br />\n<br />\n咁多人話想返學，你估真係想剩係上堂聽書咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係想同朋友一齊上堂吖！</span></span>"},{"pid":"da8738462072c1b28c99cb1c16321cbffe5ae0dc","tid":1896490,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b08fe7aad50c7b65a3e4857c4d573f62efe96d7","tid":1896490,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T0